<i>♪ Shed some light Shed
some light on me, please ♪</i>

29
00:01:18,212 --> 00:01:21,112
- How are you today?
- Good.

30
00:01:21,214 --> 00:01:22,430
Great.

31
00:01:25,786 --> 00:01:30,489
<i>The truth is hard.
The truth is awkward.</i>

32
00:01:30,574 --> 00:01:32,341
<i>And very often...</i>

33
00:01:34,711 --> 00:01:36,227
<i>the truth hurts.</i>

34
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:38,580
- Damn it!
- Bye.

35
00:01:40,450 --> 00:01:44,570
She's doing McDreamy. She's
doing McDreamy and lying about it.

36
00:01:44,672 --> 00:01:46,538
She thinks I'm weak? Fragile?

37
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,373
Like I can't handle
it because of Burke.

38
00:01:48,476 --> 00:01:52,093
- Poor Cristina. All alone.
- Damn right, poor Cristina.

39
00:01:53,998 --> 00:01:55,997
