40
00:01:57,400 --> 00:02:00,168
<i>I mean, people say
they want the truth.</i>

41
00:02:02,072 --> 00:02:04,305
<i>But do they really?</i>

42
00:02:07,444 --> 00:02:09,961
- Do I have sex hair?
