- Go ahead.
- What?

44
00:02:11,248 --> 00:02:13,916
You go ahead.
I'll wait a minute.

45
00:02:14,018 --> 00:02:17,886
So this isn't just breakup
sex, this is secret breakup sex.

46
00:02:17,988 --> 00:02:21,156
- Is this about Cristina?
- I don't know what to do.

47
00:02:21,258 --> 00:02:23,302
We don't talk about it,
the whole Burke thing.

48
00:02:23,326 --> 00:02:26,394
I want to be a good friend,
I want to take care of her,

49
00:02:26,496 --> 00:02:28,608
